    public class RegistrationDateComposite<AU extends AppUser>
extends SignupDateComposite<AU>
implements RegisterTrigger<AU>
    A SignupDateComposite that implements RegisterTrigger This is used to force an auto-created account to the registration page the first time a user logs in. Normally only makes sense when used with mandatory external auth but still capturing user meta-data at registration.
